":1849222,"uid":188406,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:46:40.000Z","msg":"∎ 200129 Super Junior 韓網新聞 ∎ <br />\n<br />\nSJ擔憂「新型肺炎」情況下兒童-青少年健康，捐贈口罩1萬個<br />\n<br />\n29日據報道，Super Junior因「新型肺炎」擴散，通過「愛心果實社會福利共同募捐會」為韓國兒童-青少年福利設施捐贈1萬個口罩，並表示「新型肺炎正在擴散，擔心免疫力弱的兒童與活動很多的青少年的健康，進行了捐贈，雖然只是很小的誠意,但希望能有所幫助。」<br />\n<br />\n&copy;️ 韓國me2day<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8163e276f2e390a0e650454ca280d7260747b348","tid":1849222,"uid":188406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vBcDm1r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvBcDm1r.jpg&h=50b971e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aLm1jN8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaLm1jN8.jpg&h=baff0f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q86phzQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ86phzQ.jpg&h=89c79ff1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZDmXCzS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZDmXCzS.jpg&h=629f0ea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WuQdVmz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWuQdVmz.jpg&h=d3c6f46f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fcb0ab04c717ccbbf2ce304f49cf64a0f651d976","tid":1849222,"uid":164961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:19:19.000Z","msg":"陷澳剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e917a2b2ec5252a5a876a41f02674ce735a482b","tid":1849222,"uid":197243,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:36:00.000Z","msg":"奶共是有代價的"},{"pid":"d71169276be78c64aede4c212d573ea0e87e6b49","tid":1849